@startuml
title Lecturer Registration & Approval Flow Diagram

|Lecturer|
start
:Open lecturer request page;
:Enter full name, email, and request reason;
:Submit lecturer account request;

|System Handler|
:Validate required fields;
:Ensure email is not already registered;
:Store request with PENDING status;

|Admin|
:Open lecturer request list;
:Review pending request details;
if (Approve request?) then (Yes)
  :Approve request;
  |System Handler|
  :Create user with LECTURER role;
  :Generate temporary password;
  :Create login account;
  :Update request to APPROVED;
  |Admin|
  :Receive temporary account credentials for handoff;
  |Lecturer|
  :Receive account credentials from Admin;
  :Log in to the system;
else (No)
  :Reject request;
  |System Handler|
  :Update request to REJECTED;
  |Lecturer|
  :Receive rejected status;
endif

stop
@enduml
